    "body": "Thanks so much @nonameb3 - turns out it's related to an additional field sent by remix/or metamask on eth_call (timestamp). This is a field that is not in the JSON RPC ethereum specification https://github.com/ethereum/eth1.0-specs/blob/05d6bf480a4e3228cf42b86b044de6832c077b3a/json-rpc/spec.json#L1624\r\nAnd it seems recent because a few weeks ago it was working.  \r\n\r\nWe can ignore this field, which we've changed in the PR linked above.\r\n",
